  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>Inspired from the already existing \"Spleef\" mini-game: Try to <strong>dig</strong> the <strong>blocks</strong> below the opposing player to make him <strong>fall</strong>, that's it!... But with:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Special powers</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Randomly generated maps</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Character customization</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Ranked mode</strong></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Powers</h2>Try to master this game by using your favorite power:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Mega Jump</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Throwing Tool</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Teleportation</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Invisibility</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547240/extras/20ad0733e7c15f4035b828b96c32f400.poster.avif?t=1765204753\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547240/extras/20ad0733e7c15f4035b828b96c32f400.webm?t=1765204753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547240/extras/20ad0733e7c15f4035b828b96c32f400.mp4?t=1765204753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maps</h2>Every map is <strong>generated randomly</strong> on runtime. You will never get bored on the same map, but try to adapt to all of them!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547240/extras/0c317e2cfbdcdf07361f44944d481a39.poster.avif?t=1765204753\" width=598 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547240/extras/0c317e2cfbdcdf07361f44944d481a39.webm?t=1765204753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><